@HillaryClinton @JoeBiden The answer's simple - we're not worthy. We're "losers," to hear @POTUS speak, because we're not rich. And, as "losers," we apparently deserve to sicken & die from #COVID19, quickly, so that we can get out of the way of the @GOP's election push. 

Monstrous.
